msgid "WPA2"
msgstr "WPA2"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12383
msgid "<ulink url=\"&wifiprotectedaccessc;\">Wi-Fi Protected Access 2</ulink>"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"&wifiprotectedaccessc;\">Wi-Fi Protected Access 2</ulink> (Accès protégé Wi-FI 2)"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12386
msgid "3rd generation wireless encryption standard (full 802.11i), non-compatible with WEP"
msgstr "troisième génération de norme de chiffrement sans fil (802.11i complète), non compatible avec WEP"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12392
msgid "The actual choice of protocol is usually limited by the wireless router you deploy."
msgstr "Le choix du protocole est normalement restreint par le routeur sans fil déployé."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12395
msgid "The wireless LAN interface with WPA/WPA2"
msgstr "L'interface de réseau local sans fil avec WPA/WPA2"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12396
msgid "You need to install the <literal>wpasupplicant</literal> package to support the WLAN with the new WPA/WPA2."
msgstr "Vous devrez installer le paquet <literal>wpasupplicant</literal> afin de prendre en compte le WLAN avec les nouveaux protocoles WPA/WPA2."

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12397 debian-reference.en.xmlt:12411
msgid "In case of the <ulink url=\"&dhcp;\">DHCP</ulink> served IP on WLAN connection, the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry should be as the following."
msgstr "Dans le cas d'IP fournies par <ulink url=\"&dhcp;\">DHCP</ulink> sur une connexion WLAN, l'entrée du fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» doit être similaire à la suivante&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12398
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"allow-hotplug ath0\n"
"iface ath0 inet dhcp\n"
" wpa-ssid homezone\n"
" # hexadecimal psk is encoded from a plaintext passphrase\n"
" wpa-psk 000102030405060708090a0b0c0d0e0f101112131415161718191a1b1c1d1e1f"
msgstr ""
"allow-hotplug ath0\n"
"iface ath0 inet dhcp\n"
" wpa-ssid zonemaison\n"
" # la clé psk hexadécimale est encodée depuis une phrase de passe en texte clair\n"
" wpa-psk 000102030405060708090a0b0c0d0e0f101112131415161718191a1b1c1d1e1f"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12403
msgid "See \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/wpasupplicant/README.modes.gz</literal>\"."
msgstr "Voir «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/wpasupplicant/README.modes.gz</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12406
msgid "The wireless LAN interface with WEP"
msgstr "L'interface réseau local sans fil avec WEP"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12407
msgid "You need to install the <literal>wireless-tools</literal> package to support the WLAN with the old WEP.  (Your consumer grade router may still be using this insecure infrastructure but this is better than nothing.)"
msgstr "Vous devrez installer le paquet <literal>wireless-tools</literal> pour prendre en charge le WLAN avec l'ancien protocole WEP. (Votre routeur grand public peut encore utiliser cette infrastructure non sûre mais c'est mieux que rien)."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><caution><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12409
msgid "Please note that your network traffic on WLAN with WEP may be sniffed by others."
msgstr "Remarquez que le trafic réseau sur votre WLAN avec WEP peut être espionné par d'autres."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12412
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"allow-hotplug eth0\n"
"iface eth0 inet dhcp\n"
" wireless-essid Home\n"
" wireless-key1 0123-4567-89ab-cdef\n"
" wireless-key2 12345678\n"
" wireless-key3 s:password\n"
" wireless-defaultkey 2\n"
" wireless-keymode open"
msgstr ""
"allow-hotplug eth0\n"
"iface eth0 inet dhcp\n"
" wireless-essid Maison\n"
" wireless-key1 0123-4567-89ab-cdef\n"
" wireless-key2 12345678\n"
" wireless-key3 s:mot_de_passe\n"
" wireless-defaultkey 2\n"
" wireless-keymode open"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12420
msgid "See \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/wireless-tools/README.Debian</literal>\"."
msgstr "Voir «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/wireless-tools/README.Debian</literal>&nbsp;»."

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12423
msgid "The PPP connection"
msgstr "La connexion PPP"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12424
msgid "You need to configure the PPP connection first as described before (see <xref linkend=\"_the_ppp_connection_with_pppconfig\"/>).  Then, add the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry for the primary PPP device <literal>ppp0</literal> as the following."
msgstr "Vous devrez d'abord configurer la connexion PPP comme décrit précédemment (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_ppp_connection_with_pppconfig\"/>). Ensuite, ajoutez dans le fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» une entrée pour le périphérique PPP primaire <literal>ppp0</literal> comme suit&nbsp;:"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12425
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"iface ppp0 inet ppp\n"
" provider &lt;isp_name&gt;"
msgstr ""
"iface ppp0 inet ppp\n"
" provider &lt;nom_fai&gt;"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12429
msgid "The alternative PPP connection"
msgstr "La connexion alternative PPP"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12430
msgid "You need to configure the alternative PPP connection with <literal>wvdial</literal> first as described before (see <xref linkend=\"_the_alternative_ppp_connection_with_wvdialconf\"/>).  Then, add the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry for the primary PPP device <literal>ppp0</literal> as the following."
msgstr "Vous devrez d'abord configurer la connexion PPP alternative avec <literal>wvdial</literal> comme décrit précédemment (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_alternative_ppp_connection_with_wvdialconf\"/>). Ajoutez ensuite dans le fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» une entrée pour le périphérique primaire PPP <literal>ppp0</literal> comme suit&nbsp;:"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12431
#, no-wrap
msgid "iface ppp0 inet wvdial"
msgstr "iface ppp0 inet wvdial"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12434
msgid "The PPPoE connection"
msgstr "La connexion PPPoE"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12435
msgid "For PC connected directly to the WAN served by the PPPoE, you need to configure system with the PPPoE connection as described before (see <xref linkend=\"_the_pppoe_connection_with_pppoeconf\"/>).  Then, add the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry for the primary PPPoE device <literal>eth0</literal> as the following."
msgstr "Pour le PC directement connecté au WAN et utilisant PPPoE, vous devez configurer votre système pour une connexion PPPoE comme cela a été décrit précédemment (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_pppoe_connection_with_pppoeconf\"/>). Ajoutez ensuite dans le fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» une entrée pour le premier périphérique PPPoE <literal>eth0</literal> comme suit&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12436
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"allow-hotplug eth0\n"
"iface eth0 inet manual\n"
" pre-up /sbin/ifconfig eth0 up\n"
" up ifup ppp0=dsl\n"
" down ifdown ppp0=dsl\n"
" post-down /sbin/ifconfig eth0 down\n"
"# The following is used internally only\n"
