# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26923
msgid "XML text looks somewhat like <ulink url=\"&html;\">HTML</ulink>.  It enables us to manage multiple formats of output for a document.  One easy XML system is the <literal>docbook-xsl</literal> package, which is used here."
msgstr "Le texte en XML ressemble un peu à <ulink url=\"&html;\">HTML</ulink>. Il vous permet de gérer de nombreux format de sortie pour un document. Un système XML facile est le paquet <literal>docbook-xsl</literal> qui est utilisé ici."

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26924
msgid "Each XML file starts with standard XML declaration as the following."
msgstr "Chaque fichier XML commence par la déclaration XML standard suivante&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26925
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26926
msgid "The basic syntax for one XML element is marked up as the following."
msgstr "La syntaxe de base d'un élément XML est balisée de la manière suivante&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26927
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"&gt;content&lt;/name&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"&gt;contenu&lt;/nom&gt;"

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26928
msgid "XML element with empty content is marked up in the following short form."
msgstr "Un élément XML dont le contenu est vide est balisé de la façon raccourcie suivante&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26929
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"/&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"/&gt;"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26930
msgid "The \"<literal>attribute=\"value\"</literal>\" in the above examples are optional."
msgstr "«&nbsp;<literal>attribute=\"value\"</literal>&nbsp;» dans les exemples ci-dessus es optionnel."

#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26931
msgid "The comment section in XML is marked up as the following."
msgstr "L'action commentaire en XML est balisée comme suit&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:26932
#, no-wrap
